          <.heading2 margin="my-5" id="space-prop-avatar-group">
            <.link patch={~p"/chelekom/docs/avatar/#space-prop-avatar-group"}>
              Space prop Avatar group
            </.link>
          </.heading2>

          <.cp>
            The space attribute in the Mishka Chelekom Avatar Group component has the following size options: <.custom_inline_code>extra_small</.custom_inline_code>, <.custom_inline_code>small</.custom_inline_code>, <.custom_inline_code>medium</.custom_inline_code>, <.custom_inline_code>large</.custom_inline_code>, <.custom_inline_code>extra_large</.custom_inline_code>, and <.custom_inline_code>none</.custom_inline_code>.
          </.cp>

